{"tid":1130782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚惠珠：修訂逃犯條例與否非靠上街抗議","createTime":"2019-04-29T09:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T10:56:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"976ee17e36bf03229133d47e1bfde540b6b95f1e","tid":1130782,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠說，立法會應該根據本身的議程審議修訂逃犯條例與法庭的判刑無關，又指是否通過修訂逃犯條例應該由立法會審議後決定，而不是靠上街抗議，被不同政見人士騎劫。<br />\n對於星期日反對修例遊行的參與人數，譚惠珠說，不同的統計有不同的數字，因此不會評論。她又指從來沒有在中央政府參與的任何會議，提過修訂逃犯條例，她亦是在傳媒的報道才知道特區政府建議修例。她不認同泛民主派提出用單次方式處理台灣殺人犯的個案，因為立法會公開討論後，疑犯就有機會逃走。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0-%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E8%88%87%E5%90%A6%E9%9D%9E%E9%9D%A0%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0-090657980.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25AD%259A%25E6%2583%25A0%25E7%258F%25A0-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2590%25A6%25E9%259D%259E%25E9%259D%25A0%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A1%2597%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0-090657980.html&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9Q9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=8b20be29\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0-%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E8%88%87%E5%90%A6%E9%9D%9E%E9%9D%A0%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0-090657980.html</a>"},{"pid":"3d03b1abc34fd1e72d33b4c0e647a896b2ecae78","tid":1130782,"uid":164050,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:27:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffc343b4a7f0d802e3ccd53b45eca46757d3a47c","tid":1130782,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"呢隻死廢老想點， 和平上街又唔得， 暴力又唔得， 咁想市民點反映不滿啊"},{"pid":"546e91b26356372446eaf2a0803a015613b01283","tid":1130782,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d03b1abc34fd1e72d33b4c0e647a896b2eca